    public class NaiveBayesModel
extends ProbabilisticClassificationModel<Vector,NaiveBayesModel>
implements MLWritable
    :: Experimental :: Model produced by NaiveBayes param: pi log of class priors, whose dimension is C (number of classes) param: theta log of class conditional probabilities, whose dimension is C (number of classes) by D (number of features)

        Description copied from class: ProbabilisticClassificationModel
        Estimate the probability of each class given the raw prediction, doing the computation in-place. These predictions are also called class conditional probabilities.
